<view class="page cancel-logs-page"><view class="section logs-header-card"><view class="logs-header-wrap"><view class="logs-header-meta"><view class="logs-header-title">协商历史记录</view><view class="logs-header-desc">记录本订单取消协商和逾期赔付处理的历史明细。</view></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="section empty-logs"><view class="empty-visual">空</view><text class="empty-text">暂无任何协商记录</text><text class="empty-subtext">本单尚未发起取消协商或逾期赔付流程。</text></view><block wx:else><view class="timeline-logs-wrap"><view wx:for="{{b}}" wx:for-item="log" wx:key="l" class="timeline-log-item"><view class="log-indicator"><view class="{{['log-dot', log.a && 'first']}}"></view><view wx:if="{{log.b}}" class="log-line"></view></view><view class="log-card-body"><view class="log-card-header"><text class="log-action-name">{{log.c}}</text><text class="log-type">{{log.d}}</text><text class="log-action-date">{{log.e}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{log.f}}" class="log-card-reason"><text class="reason-label">赔付申请：</text><text class="reason-text">{{log.g}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{log.h}}" class="log-card-reason"><text class="reason-label">事由/说明：</text><text class="reason-text">{{log.i}}</text></view><view wx:if="{{log.j}}" class="log-card-reason"><text class="reason-label">金额：</text><text class="reason-text">{{log.k}}</text></view></view></view></view></block><miniapp-login-sheet class="r" u-r="loginSheet" bindsuccess="{{d}}" u-i="ff65abe0-0" bind:__l="__l"/></view>